<section class="suds-stack">
  <div class="suds-stack__wrap">
    <div class="suds-stack__intro">
      <p class="suds-stack__eyebrow">Built to book the right service faster</p>
      <h2>Send photos, get the right package, and get your vehicle handled at home.</h2>
      <p>
        The fastest way to book is simple: send the vehicle year, make, model, city, and photos of the interior and exterior.
        Sam will recommend the correct service before you pay for the wrong level of detail.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-stack__steps">
      <article>
        <span>1</span>
        <h3>Send the vehicle</h3>
        <p>Year, make, model, city, and photos. This prevents underquoting and gets the service matched to the actual condition.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>2</span>
        <h3>Pick the right package</h3>
        <p>Basic for upkeep, Signature for most first bookings, Elite Reset for neglected vehicles, Ceramic for protection.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>3</span>
        <h3>Book the mobile appointment</h3>
        <p>Suds Auto Salon comes to your home, office, apartment, or approved service location around the Seattle area.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-stack__split">
      <div>
        <p class="suds-stack__eyebrow">Premium add-ons</p>
        <h2>Raise the result when the vehicle needs more.</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Pet hair removal for heavy dog hair and trapped debris.</li>
          <li>Stain extraction for seats, carpets, and family vehicle spills.</li>
          <li>Odor treatment for lingering cabin smells.</li>
          <li>Paint enhancement for better gloss and cleaner reflections.</li>
          <li>Ceramic protection for easier washing and longer-term defense.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="suds-stack__quote">
        <h3>Best value path</h3>
        <p><strong>First visit:</strong> Signature Detail or Elite Reset.</p>
        <p><strong>Upgrade:</strong> Exterior protection or paint enhancement.</p>
        <p><strong>Aftercare:</strong> Monthly maintenance plan starting at $150+.</p>
        <a href="/pages/contact">Request a Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-stack__reviews">
      <article>
        <p>"He came to my house with all that he needed. Highly recommend Sam and Suds Auto Salon."</p>
        <strong>Stacy K. - Edmonds, WA</strong>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p>"He got old stains out of the seats and thoroughly cleaned every nook and cranny."</p>
        <strong>Dane U. - Seattle, WA</strong>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p>"My car interior was done with great detail, it looks better than when I got it at the dealer."</p>
        <strong>Alinafe M. - Lake Forest Park, WA</strong>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .suds-stack {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111111;
  }

  .suds-stack__wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 20px;
  }

  .suds-stack__intro {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .suds-stack__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #8c6b05;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .suds-stack h2 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 5.4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-stack h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-stack p,
  .suds-stack li {
    color: #292929;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .suds-stack__steps,
  .suds-stack__reviews {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 34px;
  }

  .suds-stack__steps article,
  .suds-stack__reviews article,
  .suds-stack__quote {
    border: 1px solid #dedede;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: #f7f7f7;
  }

  .suds-stack__steps span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #111111;
    color: #f2d36b;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .suds-stack__split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.35fr) minmax(280px, .65fr);
    gap: 22px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 44px;
    padding: 34px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #111111;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .suds-stack__split p,
  .suds-stack__split li {
    color: #eeeeee;
  }

  .suds-stack__split ul {
    margin: 18px 0 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .suds-stack__quote {
    background: #1b170d;
    border-color: #f2d36b;
  }

  .suds-stack__quote a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding: 13px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #f2d36b;
    color: #090909;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .suds-stack__reviews strong {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 14px;
    color: #111111;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
    .suds-stack__steps,
    .suds-stack__reviews,
    .suds-stack__split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .suds-stack__wrap {
      padding: 44px 18px;
    }

    .suds-stack__split {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Suds revenue stack",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Suds revenue stack"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
